{"tid":1353501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[打氣post] 4月涂謹申主持法案委員會個陣 大家有冇諗過會變成咁","createTime":"2019-07-23T03:31:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T00:23:01.000Z","uid":2617,"like":98,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"92c791cd1f9c5ce851bd0c2a2161d40efd2140a1","tid":1353501,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:31:33.000Z","msg":"呢排有朋友話無力感好重<br />\n特別係經過星期日單恐襲之後更加攰<br />\n係呢到我想帶大家去番4月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4月17日：逃犯條例委員會召開第一次會議。委員會主持由年資最高的議員，即民主黨的涂謹申擔任。會議原先的議程為選出委員會主席，泛民主派提出規程問題，要求先行在會上討論。建制派議員則批評泛民主派「拉布」；當中工聯會的郭偉強議員更批評涂謹申「扮垃圾」，質疑他主持會議不力。涂謹申以言論屬冒犯為由，要求郭收回此言論；但郭沒有收回，涂謹申最終逐其出會議廳。歷時兩小時的第一次會議未能選出法案委員會主席。 <br />\n<br />\n當時睇番whatsapp我係咁樣形容:<br />\n「今次泛民得意wor 咁都偷到一次雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n不過我諗當時大家可能同我一樣<br />\n覺得<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後咪又係「選到主席」「條bill實過」「等死」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n但係之後我地一步一步行落黎<br />\n立法會打大交 真係選唔到主席<br />\n件事開始煲起 好多聯署醞釀<br />\n之後到6月9號大遊行 (再之後不詳述大家都知)<br />\n<br />\n大遊行 圍政總 圍立法會 圍警總<br />\n衝立法會 地區行動<br />\n行到黎呢一步 雖然越來越黑暗<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但係我相信正因為越黎越暗<br />\n光明一定係越黎越近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n政權越打壓你 證明佢好撚恐懼 代表大家做緊既方向係正確<br />\n<br />\n所以當你覺得攰 當你覺得無力<br />\n感到灰心唔知做咩好個陣<br />\n回想番由4月開始成件事點發展<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">71立法會義海豪情式救戰士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n721上環響徹雲霄既「光復香港時代革命」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n各路英雄要相信自己 <br />\n亦都相信各位同行既戰士<br />\n引用義海豪情歌詞<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「遇著苦難亦堅守同盟 情義不會淡 即使地陷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」</span></span><br />\n繼續努力 唔好放棄 齊上齊落<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">為理念而戰既人<br />\n最終一定會戰勝為金錢而戰既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n謝謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23eb2f0b8971783f6ce39552d4b371c3e7157c17","tid":1353501,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:33:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e58db0b854601c23a04c86f1318ebbeea9edc841","tid":1353501,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:35:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdfd3dfdefd7cc2c5b2a40ecd5134fc02c7c6929","tid":1353501,"uid":249608,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:36:59.000Z","msg":"真，6.9果時一齊去遊行既朋友，全部都覺得送中一定過，無論幾多人上街<br />\n香港人真係唔好妄自菲薄"},{"pid":"a7398bddc68651ff08d480053ab92d8fa3e66dc1","tid":1353501,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdfd3dfdefd7cc2c5b2a40ecd5134fc02c7c6929","tid":1353501,"uid":249608,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:36:59.000Z","msg":"真，6.9果時一齊去遊行既朋友，全部都覺得送中一定過，無論幾多人上街<br />\n香港人真係唔好妄自菲薄"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:38:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67e352f54da89cdfa35d1a2671a504e970b88ef7","tid":1353501,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdfd3dfdefd7cc2c5b2a40ecd5134fc02c7c6929","tid":1353501,"uid":249608,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:36:59.000Z","msg":"真，6.9果時一齊去遊行既朋友，全部都覺得送中一定過，無論幾多人上街<b